{{sticker:zombie-brand-clap}} 

Looks like someone found a hidden feature! They were able to do that goldish text by using a /me command before the text. It's kind of similar to old school chat emotes! 

This feature seems like something that was left in the code, since removing chunks like that can take quite a bit of effort, so it was left in! I'm not 100% sure if this is permanent 'feature' or not, so don't be surprised if it happens to not work one day.
